OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fafternoon showers dying out leaving a
OL,7,Ffine and dry evening with plenty of
OL,8,Flate sunshine. Generally clear skies
OL,9,Fovernight with the odd patch of mist
OL,10,Fand fog developing in Cornwall. Light
OL,11,Fnortherly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FEarly morning mist and fog
OL,14,Fquickly clearing to leave a fine day
OL,15,Fwith patchy cloud and light winds.
OL,16,FFeeling warm in the susnhine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
